text: Ekaterina Zubacheva is a Russian water polo player. She played for the Russian women's national water polo team in the 2006 Women's European Water Polo Championships, 2007 World Aquatics Championships, and 2009 World Aquatics Championships. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Russian water polo players
